text.tspan: On the wall to the north are etched 3 geometric shapes:
a square, a circle, and a triangle.

tspan.tspan: If you have the Silver Shapes, the door opens N.

text.tspan: "What can bind the mightiest foes?" [SPECTRE SNARE]
A random party member is +POSS, forcing Party Combat.
"Death to those who would attack the mighty one!"
There is a pool of boiling liquid here. [Dive in]
